        <abstract>
            <p>Thinks WB’s proposal a very good one. CD could suggest two or three subjects for essays with respect to the vegetable kingdom, but they would require a long course of experiments "&amp; unfortunately there is hardly any one in this country who seems inclined to devote himself to experiments".</p>
